entries.s_43: Who's there? Oh, hey! You aren't a Meatlump. I don't want to be a Meatlump. We have so much in common. I left my bag and strongbox in the cave, though. Will you go get them for me? I can't go any further inside.
entries.s_47: Oh. Then do I stay and get my stuff, but remain a Meatlump? Or do I leave and no longer be a Meatlump, but also no longer have my stuff. Hmmm.
entries.s_48: Hey, my bag! And my strongbox! Thank you. Now, if only I had something to put inside of these...
entries.s_49: Please find my bag and my strongbox. They are in the cave. Somewhere. I don't remember where I left them.
